description: The BEST Vegan Chocolate Cheesecake featuring crunchy, buttery, cookie crust with rich, creamy, velvety smooth and super chocolatey cheesecake filling. This easy no bake vegan cheesecake is quick to make and keeps for ages so you can prepare it well ahead when entertaining. Directions for a scaled down smaller version also included for those not feeding a crowd. No-one will have a clue this is vegan!
name: Vegan Chocolate Cheesecake
